ns:**\n    70→- Both stories had been stuck at `verifying` across multiple sessions due to Docker infra issues.\n    71→- Tagging cli-verifiable stories as unit-testable is the correct fix — these should never have required Docker.\n    72→\n    73→### 15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing — create-story (2026-03-25T06:50Z)\n    74→\n    75→**Problems encountered:**\n    76→- None. Story file already existed from prior planning session.\n    77→\n    78→**Risks identified:**\n    79→- `patches/error-handling/` directory doesn't exist yet — needs to be created.\n    80→- AC1 references code-review subagent integration but is tagged cli-verifiable — borderline.\n    81→\n    82→**Observations:**\n    83→- Story was pre-created. Verification tags already present and correct.\n    84→\n    85→### 15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing — dev-story (2026-03-25T06:55Z)\n    86→\n    87→**Problems encountered:**\n    88→- `src/lib/scanner.ts` listed in story but has no Semgrep integration — actual Semgrep logic lives in `src/modules/observability/analyzer.ts`.\n    89→\n    90→**Workarounds applied:**\n    91→- Semgrep test fixtures use annotation format but can only validate with semgrep installed. Vitest tests validate file existence/content only.\n    92→\n    93→**Code quality concerns:**\n    94→- `no-bare-except-ellipsis` rule uses Semgrep `...` metavariable — matches ALL except bodies, not just literal Ellipsis. Correct per AC1 but name misleading.\n    95→- Hook grep pattern `except Exception.*pass` is approximate — matches comments/strings too.\n    96→\n    97→**Observations:**\n    98→- All 3799 tests pass. Zero regressions.\n    99→\n   100→### 15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing — code-review (2026-03-25T07:02Z)\n   101→\n   102→**Bugs found and fixed:**\n   103→- HIGH: Hook grep pattern `except Exception.*pass` never matches multiline Python syntax (AC2 was non-functional). Fixed with awk-based multiline detection.\n   104→- HIGH: Semgrep `no-bare-ex